- Style correction for CTF: adding a period after the number and emphasized the object names.
- Bib style has been updated.

v. 1.3 (Jun 30, 2023)
- After reviewing from Graduate School, some formatting issues have been fixed in more accodance with the ETD style guideline.

v. 1.4 (Oct 2, 2023)
- Adopting 2023 ETD Style
link: https://graduatestudies.uoregon.edu/sites/default/files/2023-07/2023-style-manual.pdf

